lic","site_admin":false},"node_id":"MDc6UmVsZWFzZTQ5MDM0NjQ0","tag_name":"v0.7-1","target_commitish":"main","name":"Version 0.7-1","draft":false,"immutable":false,"prerelease":false,"created_at":"2021-09-05T17:18:55Z","updated_at":"2021-09-05T17:22:30Z","published_at":"2021-09-05T17:22:30Z","assets":[],"tarball_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/foonathan/memory/tarball/v0.7-1","zipball_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/foonathan/memory/zipball/v0.7-1","body":"Just bugfixes:\r\n\r\n* CMake: automatically link libatomic on platforms where that is necessary (#95)\r\n* catch small block sizes of `memory_pool` (#113)\r\n* fix buffer overflow in `memory_pool_collection`'s array allocation (#99)\r\n* fix compatibility with Windows UWP (#102)\r\n* fix computation of `memory_pool::min_block_size` (#110)\r\n* fix debug assertion in free lists (#111)\r\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/foonathan/memory/releases/49034644/reactions","total_count":4,"+1":4,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/foonathan/memory/releases/34693086","assets_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/foonathan/memory/releases/34693086/assets","upload_url":"https://uploads.github.com/repos/foonathan/memory/releases/34693086/assets{?name,label}","html_url":"https://github.com/foonathan/memory/releases/tag/v0.7","id":34693086,"author":{"login":"foonathan","id":9192733,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjkxOTI3MzM=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/9192733?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan","html_url":"https://github.com/foonathan","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"node_id":"MDc6UmVsZWFzZTM0NjkzMDg2","tag_name":"v0.7","target_commitish":"master","name":"Version 0.7","draft":false,"immutable":false,"prerelease":false,"created_at":"2020-12-02T13:32:19Z","updated_at":"2020-12-02T14:03:19Z","published_at":"2020-12-02T14:03:19Z","assets":[],"tarball_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/foonathan/memory/tarball/v0.7","zipball_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/foonathan/memory/zipball/v0.7","body":"BREAKING: Removed the use of the compatibility library to automatically generate macros and workaround for older compilers. The important compatibility workarounds like the `__builtin_clz` extension are still used, but workarounds for missing C++11 library features have been removed. In particular, the library now requires compiler support for `noexcept`, `constexpr`, `alignof` and `thread_local`.This means that GCC 4.8 and Visual Studio version 12.0 (both released in 2013), are no longer supported.\r\n\r\n## Adapter\r\n\r\nBREAKING: Remove `Mutex` support from `allocator_reference` and consequently from `std_allocator`, `allocator_deleter`, etc. Embedding the `Mutex` with the reference was *fundamentally* broken and unusable to ensure thread safety. Use a reference to a `thread_safe_allocator` instead, which actually guarantees thread safety.\r\n\r\n## Allocator\r\n\r\nAdd ability to query the minimal block size required by a `memory_pool` or `memory_stack` that should contain the given memory. Due to internal data structures and debug fences this is more than the naive memory request, so it can be computed now.\r\n\r\n## Bugfixes\r\n\r\n* more CMake improvements for cross-compiling, among others\r\n* bugfixes to support UWP (#80), VxWorks (#81) and QNX (#85, #88, among others)\r\n* better support missing container node size (#59, #72, among others)\r\n* fix alignment issues in debug mode\r\n* fix tracking for allocators without block allocators"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/foonathan/memory/releases/20427890","assets_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/foonathan/memory/releases/20427890/assets","upload_url":"https://uploads.github.com/repos/foonathan/memory/releases/20427890/assets{?name,label}","html_url":"https://github.com/foonathan/memory/releases/tag/v0.6-2","id":20427890,"author":{"login":"foonathan","id":9192733,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjkxOTI3MzM=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/9192733?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan","html_url":"https://github.com/foonathan","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"node_id":"MDc6UmVsZWFzZTIwNDI3ODkw","tag_name":"v0.6-2","target_commitish":"master","name":"Version 0.6-2","draft":false,"immutable":false,"prerelease":false,"created_at":"2019-10-02T19:13:49Z","updated_at":"2019-10-02T20:35:03Z","published_at":"2019-10-02T20:35:03Z","assets":[],"tarball_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/foonathan/memory/tarball/v0.6-2","zipball_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/foonathan/memory/zipball/v0.6-2","body":"Vario