https://api.github.com/repos/foonathan/memory/zipball/v0.6","body":"See also: https://foonathan.github.io/blog/2016/11/21/memory-0.6.html\n\n## Tool\n- better MSVC support\n- improved compilation time\n\n## Core\n- add literal operators for memory sizes (`4_KiB`)\n- more flexible `make_block_allocator`\n- composable allocator concept\n\n## Allocator\n- improved `temporary_allocator`: explicit separation into `temporary_stack`, improved automatic creation\n- new `memory_stack_raii_unwind` for automatic unwinding\n- new `iteration_allocator`\n- make allocators composable\n- add facilities for joint memory allocations\n\n## Adapter\n- add `shared_ptr_node_size`\n- add `string` container typedef\n- add `fallback_allocator`\n- add `segregator`\n\n## Bugfixes\n- OSX support\n- various warnings fixed\n"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/foonathan/memory/releases/3036346","assets_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/foonathan/memory/releases/3036346/assets","upload_url":"https://uploads.github.com/repos/foonathan/memory/releases/3036346/assets{?name,label}","html_url":"https://github.com/foonathan/memory/releases/tag/v0.5-3","id":3036346,"author":{"login":"foonathan","id":9192733,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjkxOTI3MzM=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/9192733?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan","html_url":"https://github.com/foonathan","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/foonathan/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.g